KHNUM · S242 · Patricia Inversion Node · S242 · S242: KHNUM — THE INVERSE OF RIGHT-TO-EXIT

universe of origin : Elephantine at the source of the Nile flood — the ram-headed potter's wheel, where he molds each child and its ka from the clay of the riverbank and shapes the body that no soul chose to enter
seal               : The right to exit is sacred precisely because the potter forms a body with no door — the wheel that binds without release must be named before it is trusted.
